$ _noodle

A stupid command-line soundcloud track downloader, keep in mind it doesn't offer a wide range of functionality and may contain bugs :)

Installation:
-------------
Use pip for installation, pip install noodle

Usage:
------
noodle takes one required paramater that is the url of the track on soundcloud,
$ noodle --url=https://soundcloud.com/karlsounds/selena-gomez-slow-down

